descriptor.short_desc: Vicks VapoRub contains menthol, camphor and eucalyptus oil, known for their therapeutic benefits in cough and cold relief. It provides effective multi-symptom relief from 6 symptoms- blocked nose, breathing difficulty, cough, body ache, headache & muscular stiffness directions: apply on chest, throat and back for relief from 6 cold symptoms: breathing difficulty, body ache, cough, blocked nose, headache and muscular stiffness. Start feeling relief in 5 minutes from cough, blocked nose and breathing difficulty.
descriptor.long_desc: Composition Content/100g: Pudinah Ke Phool 2.82g, Kapoor 5.25g, Ajowan Ke Phool 0.10g, Tarpin Ka Tel 5.57ml, Nilgiri Tel 1.49ml, Jatiphal Tel 0.54ml, Base Q.S. Features It provides effective multi-symptom relief from 6 symptoms- blocked nose, breathing difficulty, cough, body ache, headache & muscular stiffness throat and back for relief from 6 cold symptoms: breathing difficulty, body ache, cough, blocked nose, headache and muscular stiffness. Start feeling relief in 5 minutes from cough, blocked nose and breathing difficulty. How to Use Apply on chest and throat, temporarily relieves cough due to common cold, on muscles and joints, temporarily relieves minor aches and pains. Add 1-2 teaspoons to a bowl of hot water (not boiling). Cover head with a towel.

descriptor.name: Volini Pain Relief Spray - Long Lasting (Prescription Required - No, Usage Instruction - Spray 2-3 seconds and Massage gently) by Health & Wellness Store
descriptor.short_desc: Volini is the No. 1 Pain Reliever Brand prescribed and recommended by doctors, and trusted by millions of consumers to beat pain. It is a modern day pain reliever, scientifically formulated for effective pain relief which is used for joint pain, back pain, neck pain, shoulder pain, sprains and strains. Only Volini Gel has a quick absorb nanogel formula which makes the product absorb quickly and goes deep to provide quick and long lasting relief, without massaging.
descriptor.long_desc: Composition Diclofenac diethylamine BP-1.16% w/w (equivalent to diclofenac sodium 1% w/w) Linseed Oil BP (Oleum Lini)-3% w/w Methyl salicylate IP-10% w/w Menthol IP-5% w/w Excipients & Propellant q.s. to-100% w/w How to Use The spray can should be shaken well before each use. The contents should be sprayed from 5 cm distance on the affected areas. Adult: 3-4 times a day, Children: 2-3 times, under adult supervision. Volini should be applied only to intact skin surfaces and not to skin wounds or open injuries. It must not come in contact with eyes or mucous membranes either, and must not be ingested.
